msgstr "ລົບລ້າງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຖືກຈັດດັດຊະນີ"

#: src/cli/main.c:74 src/cli/tracker-search.c:397
msgid "Search for content"
msgstr "ຄົ້ນຫາເນື້ອຫາ"

